### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Confirmer un paiement (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_id": "payment-uuid-here",
  "payment_method": "mobile_money",
  "receipt_url": "https://example.com/receipt.pdf"
}

### Test 2 - Confirmer un paiement minimal
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_id": "payment-uuid-here"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: payment_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 4 - Erreur: paiement déjà confirmé
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_id": "already-paid-payment-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: paiement annulé
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_id": "cancelled-payment-uuid"
}

